{"prompt": "Generate a website for a edtech platform. The website should be corporate and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EdTech Innovations</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #E53935; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #f8bbba; /* Lighter shade of red */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --header-footer-bg: #f44336; /* Slightly darker red */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 15px 0 0 0;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 70px 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            border-color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .features-section {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #f9f9f9;\n        }\n\n        .features-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .features-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .about-section {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--secondary-color), var(--brand-color));\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .about-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .about-section p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>EdTech Innovations</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#features\">Features</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About Us</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n        <h2>Transforming Education, Empowering Learners</h2>\n        <p>Revolutionary learning solutions designed for the future of education. Accessible, engaging, and effective.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\" class=\"features-section\">\n        <h2>Our Core Offerings</h2>\n        <div class=\"features-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Personalized Learning Paths</h3>\n                <p>Tailored curricula that adapt to individual student paces and learning styles, ensuring optimal engagement and comprehension.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n              